OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fgradually die out this evening.
OL,7,FTurning cloudier through the early
OL,8,Fhours, with rain spreading in from the
OL,9,Fwest towards the end of the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FAn overcast and wet morning,
OL,12,Fthe rain occasionally heavy. Brighter
OL,13,Fspells and showers developing for the
OL,14,Fafternoon, some likely heavy at times.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,17,FVariable amounts of cloud with a good
OL,18,Fdeal of dry weather but a few showers
OL,19,Fnot to be ruled out. Becoming often
OL,20,Fwarm or very warm in sunny intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
